EIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Mnemos.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">58.28</biblScope> </bibl>) <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἱαρὰ τᾶς Ἥρας</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.517</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (Argos, <date TEIform=\"date\">v B.C.</date>); [<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀναγράψαι εἰς ς]τήλην λευκοῦ λίθου [κα]ὶ ἀναθ[εῖναι αὐτὴν ἐπὶ τελα]μ[ῶ]νος</foreign> prob. rest. in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ CIG\">CIG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2056d</biblScope> </bibl> (loc.inc., perh. Odessus); simply <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">στήλη, ἀναγράψαι . . εἰς τελαμῶνα λευκοῦ λίθου καὶ ἀναθεῖναι κτλ</ref></xr>. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ SIG\">SIG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">731.41</biblScope> </bibl> (Tomi, <date TEIform=\"date\">i B.C.</date>), al., cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Milet.\">Milet.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3p.377No.</biblScope> </bibl> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">153.39</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ BMus.Inscr.\">BMus.Inscr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1007</biblScope> </bibl> (Cyzicus, <date TEIform=\"date\">ii A.D.</date>), etc.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}